	   <tr><td colspan=2>It's from the HOLE....the HOLE!!!!<br>I don't expect to ever go there this year...and I'm almost high enough level...to me this place is almost legendary...when I first started, and I heard about "The Hole" and how hard it was to get in, and I guess out, and how high you had to be (this was after Kunark, because I had the expansion, but before Velious)...before Velious...this WAS Veeshan's Temple....this was the Kael Drakkel...now it's just a high level Lavastorm (I imagine Druids and AntiSummon casters would rule here!)...also find it funny that an enchanter in Illusion: Elemental would be amiable here! hilarious.....anyway...what I'm trying to say is....It should be an honor to have any item from this zone...I imagine a raid on this zone would be figured out a week in advance...just the way I see the zone...if I had the money, and someone was selling this, I'd jump on it faster than you can say "why would a druid want this?"...'nuff said<br><br>(btw, not seeing maps of this place until just recently, and never hearing any info about this zone, please forgive my lack of knowledge about this unknown zone..do you think you'll ever get there?)<br>&nbsp;<br>Astralyte, Druid 37 - Xev<br>Astrall,VS Beastlord - Xev</td></tr>
